com.interpss.core.net

Interface Area

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, RegDeviceContainer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AreaImpl

    public interface Area
extends RegDeviceContainer
    A representation of the model object 'Area'. Area is a name tagged element, optional containng a list of zones. It is identified in the network container by its areaNumber.

    The following features are supported:

    • Inter Swing Bus Id
    • Alter Swing Bus Name
    • Inter Exp Power
    • Inter Err
    • Code
    • Network
    • Zone List
    See Also:
    NetPackage.getArea()
